Test cases:
1)  --segfault option causes segfault
2)  --segfault combined with --catch properly catches segfault
3)  --catch option exits cleanly
4)  --catch option copies stdin to stdout properly
5)  --input from a good file causes no errors
6)  --input from a file copies to stdout properly
5)  --input from a good file and output to a file causes no errors
6)  --input from a file copies to an output file properly
7)  input from stdin to a good output file causes no errors
8)  input from stdin properly copies to an output file